imdb.plot outline: Each week, MotoMan - part car guy, part comedian and part storyteller - experiences everything from going behind the scenes to build a major manufacturer's show car to piloting the Goodyear Blimp to learning how to drift from the number one pro-drifter.
imdb.title: MotoMan
